WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:00:12.640 --> 00:00:13.800
{\an8}I'm useless.

00:00:20.840 --> 00:00:21.920
{\an8}Husniya Radwa.

00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:26.880
{\an8}You're perfect for me.

00:00:31.560 --> 00:00:33.080
{\an8}Will you...

00:00:35.440 --> 00:00:37.080
{\an8}Will you marry me?

00:00:42.280 --> 00:00:43.720
For what reason?

00:00:46.880 --> 00:00:49.440
Because you are my first and last love.

00:00:51.920 --> 00:00:54.279
Between your first and last,

00:00:54.280 --> 00:00:57.239
how many women have you fallen in love with?

00:00:57.240 --> 00:00:58.880
None.

00:01:00.240 --> 00:01:01.080
No one.

00:01:07.360 --> 00:01:10.319
I have so many problems in my life, Ridz.

00:01:10.320 --> 00:01:12.079
I have problems in here.

00:01:12.080 --> 00:01:14.880
Problems with my head, my heart and my soul.

00:01:16.280 --> 00:01:20.200
There's nothing in it for you if you marry me, Ridz.

00:01:22.160 --> 00:01:24.200
I know you have your flaws.

00:01:25.840 --> 00:01:28.240
- Yeah, and you are Mr. Perfect. - Never.

00:01:31.760 --> 00:01:33.520
Never, unless...

00:01:35.840 --> 00:01:37.320
Unless you marry me.

00:01:59.120 --> 00:02:02.800
I've imagined you asking this a thousand times in my head.

00:02:06.360 --> 00:02:11.280
Every time you asked, I answered, "Yes."

00:02:19.360 --> 00:02:23.720
But you weren't there when I really needed you, Ridz.

00:03:16.600 --> 00:03:18.920
Ridz, where were you?

00:03:24.520 --> 00:03:28.119
How could you turn away the moment you saw me

00:03:28.120 --> 00:03:29.479
and not come inside?

00:03:29.480 --> 00:03:32.560
That just shows that you're disrespectful. Your son is so rude.

00:03:33.680 --> 00:03:36.279
I'm going back to the office. I left something.

00:03:36.280 --> 00:03:39.279
What did you leave that's so important you tried to avoid me?

00:03:39.280 --> 00:03:40.479
I must've forgotten my manners, Auntie.

00:03:40.480 --> 00:03:42.640
I hope I don't offend you again.

00:03:44.040 --> 00:03:47.559
You said you were bringing a daughter-in-law for your mom.

00:03:47.560 --> 00:03:49.239
- So where is she? - Right.

00:03:49.240 --> 00:03:50.800
She's around.

00:03:51.400 --> 00:03:53.519
Probably playing hide-and-seek. Why don't you close your eyes?

00:03:53.520 --> 00:03:57.159
Count to ten, then open your eyes. Maybe she's in the drain.

00:03:57.160 --> 00:04:01.279
Ridz, why can't you just marry me?

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:03.039
I'm perfect for you.

00:04:03.040 --> 00:04:06.519
The Prophet said we should choose a wife based on four criteria.

00:04:06.520 --> 00:04:10.479
Faith, beauty, wealth, and lineage.

00:04:10.480 --> 00:04:11.720
I'm pretty.

00:04:12.520 --> 00:04:14.039
Radwa is pretty.

00:04:14.040 --> 00:04:15.920
She's perfectly religious.

00:04:16.519 --> 00:04:18.359
Not like you. You miss your prayers.

00:04:18.360 --> 00:04:21.199
You never fast and you dye your hair.

00:04:21.200 --> 00:04:22.720
You're at the first stage of learning the Quran.

00:04:23.480 --> 00:04:26.680
So now you see why I never chose you.

00:04:28.080 --> 00:04:30.880
Ridz, you shouldn't insult Aina that way.

00:04:31.480 --> 00:04:32.560
I feel offended.

00:04:33.200 --> 00:04:34.480
You can go.

00:04:36.880 --> 00:04:38.320
If you are offended, go home!

00:04:39.920 --> 00:04:41.240
Stop it, Ridz.

00:04:41.840 --> 00:04:43.800
That was too much, Ridz.

00:04:48.600 --> 00:04:50.199
I'm sorry, Mom.

00:04:50.200 --> 00:04:51.999
What's going on?

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:54.800
I've never seen you act like this.

00:04:58.280 --> 00:04:59.400
It's Radwa.

00:05:00.480 --> 00:05:02.040
What about her?

00:05:03.800 --> 00:05:05.920
I proposed to her, but she...

00:05:07.920 --> 00:05:09.360
She said no.

00:05:12.400 --> 00:05:16.839
So you're in shock that she rejected you?

00:05:16.840 --> 00:05:18.280
That's not it.

00:05:19.720 --> 00:05:21.600
But I never thought

00:05:24.160 --> 00:05:26.680
it would hurt this much, Mom.

00:05:32.840 --> 00:05:35.520
I guess this is how she felt when I left her before.

00:05:37.560 --> 00:05:39.279
Don't worry, sweetie.

00:05:39.280 --> 00:05:41.120
Don't cry.

00:05:43.160 --> 00:05:45.000
Come on, let's go inside.

00:05:45.760 --> 00:05:47.160
Come on.

00:06:08.120 --> 00:06:12.480
Why do you keep checking on me every five minutes?

00:06:21.360 --> 00:06:24.319
You have got it wrong if you're trying to show he's pious.

00:06:24.320 --> 00:06:27.560
The qibla is that way.

00:06:31.720 --> 00:06:36.960
He came to discuss your engagement.

00:06:43.720 --> 00:06:44.640
I don't want to.

00:06:48.680 --> 00:06:52.959
Listen, Radwa. You got fired.

00:06:52.960 --> 00:06:54.879
Bear this in mind.

00:06:54.880 --> 00:06:57.599
This house, water, electricity,

00:06:57.600 --> 00:07:01.199
my phone bill, your sisters', student loans,

00:07:01.200 --> 00:07:04.440
and your dad's medication all come with a price tag.

00:07:10.360 --> 00:07:12.359
If you don't mind,

00:07:12.360 --> 00:07:13.440
I can cover those expenses.

00:07:14.760 --> 00:07:19.600
Don't worry, since you're not working, let me make the payments.

00:07:20.360 --> 00:07:21.640
Are you sure about that?

00:07:23.600 --> 00:07:24.600
Don't you see?

00:07:25.800 --> 00:07:28.199
He's nobody yet in your life,

00:07:28.200 --> 00:07:30.079
and yet he offers to help our family.

00:07:30.080 --> 00:07:32.159
Do you think you can find anyone else like him?

00:07:32.160 --> 00:07:33.840
He's selfless.

00:07:34.720 --> 00:07:37.919
Yes, Zafir is not stingy with money, Mom.

00:07:37.920 --> 00:07:41.319
That is why he can easily pay for escorts to keep him company at night.

00:07:41.320 --> 00:07:42.440
Radwa!

00:07:45.160 --> 00:07:47.360
Watch what you say.

00:07:47.960 --> 00:07:50.079
He is my guest right now.

00:07:50.080 --> 00:07:52.240
How could you say such things about him?

00:07:53.760 --> 00:07:55.560
If you'll excuse me, ma'am.

00:07:57.080 --> 00:07:59.440
Take care of yourself, Husniya.

00:08:00.280 --> 00:08:01.760
I love you, Husniya.

00:08:10.560 --> 00:08:11.959
Are you happy now?

00:08:11.960 --> 00:08:16.720
All you ever do is embarrass me in front of other people.

00:08:17.760 --> 00:08:19.439
You are truly evil!

00:08:19.440 --> 00:08:21.280
You're extremely rude!

00:08:22.360 --> 00:08:28.239
You should've died before you were even born!

00:08:28.240 --> 00:08:31.680
But who conceived me?

00:08:32.919 --> 00:08:34.439
Was it me?

00:08:34.440 --> 00:08:37.679
- Was it my fault? - You insolent child!

00:08:41.880 --> 00:08:43.000
Listen up.

00:08:44.400 --> 00:08:47.120
Tonight, you're going to sleep downstairs.

00:08:47.840 --> 00:08:50.679
I want you to clean this whole house.

00:08:50.680 --> 00:08:53.760
If you don't want to end up being my maid,

00:08:55.120 --> 00:08:56.680
then you'd better marry him.

00:09:08.160 --> 00:09:13.320
<i>You should've died before you came out of my womb!</i>

00:09:34.520 --> 00:09:35.960
<i>Will you...</i>

00:09:38.440 --> 00:09:40.040
<i>marry me?</i>

00:09:42.200 --> 00:09:45.200
<i>Because you are my first and last love.</i>

00:09:46.680 --> 00:09:51.320
<i>Morning. Noon. Day and night.</i>

00:09:52.040 --> 00:09:54.320
<i>I really love you, Radwa.</i>

00:10:06.480 --> 00:10:08.760
What is this?

00:10:16.560 --> 00:10:19.080
Help! Help me!

00:10:38.840 --> 00:10:40.520
You're awake.

00:10:41.600 --> 00:10:43.439
Where am I?

00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:46.279
I want to go home. Please let me go.

00:10:46.280 --> 00:10:49.479
I'm Wan Salmah. You can call me Ms. Wan.

00:10:49.480 --> 00:10:52.760
Master says that you're a fan of fried chicken.

00:10:54.160 --> 00:10:56.040
Miss, no! Miss!

00:10:56.720 --> 00:10:58.520
Let me go!

00:11:01.280 --> 00:11:03.880
Master has told us to make sure you don't run away.

00:11:04.480 --> 00:11:05.800
If you don't listen to us...

00:11:06.440 --> 00:11:07.320
Syed.

00:11:12.720 --> 00:11:16.199
Look, we'll break Ms. Wan's arms one by one.

00:11:16.200 --> 00:11:17.799
Not only her.

00:11:17.800 --> 00:11:20.720
We'll break all the servants' arms in front of you.

00:11:21.480 --> 00:11:23.360
So you'll be responsible for that.

00:11:28.200 --> 00:11:29.680
Eat.

00:11:32.480 --> 00:11:33.600
Miss.

00:11:34.680 --> 00:11:37.399
No! Please!

00:11:37.400 --> 00:11:39.040
Please!

00:12:09.960 --> 00:12:11.640
But you weren't there

00:12:13.480 --> 00:12:16.080
when I really needed you.

00:12:29.640 --> 00:12:31.919
Radwa!

00:12:31.920 --> 00:12:34.319
Where is my Cinderella?

00:12:34.320 --> 00:12:36.519
Oh, my beloved friend,

00:12:36.520 --> 00:12:38.279
what are you doing?

00:12:38.280 --> 00:12:41.120
Can't you see? I'm doing a TikTok dance.

00:12:47.320 --> 00:12:48.959
You're so funny.

00:12:48.960 --> 00:12:52.000
I'm laughing inside.

00:12:53.400 --> 00:12:54.679
What do you want, Lia?

00:12:54.680 --> 00:12:57.199
That question is very annoying.

00:12:57.200 --> 00:12:59.519
Don't you have a home, Lia?

00:12:59.520 --> 00:13:01.040
I see you here far too often.

00:13:02.680 --> 00:13:04.400
Radwa, go and get changed.

00:13:05.120 --> 00:13:06.439
You're going out with Zafir

00:13:06.440 --> 00:13:08.720
to buy stuff for your engagement.

00:13:10.240 --> 00:13:12.400
Zafir? I thought it was Adib.

00:13:12.960 --> 00:13:16.439
Are you some pimp? Swapping your daughter's partners?

00:13:16.440 --> 00:13:18.719
- Watch your mouth, girl. - Okay, I'll stop talking.

00:13:18.720 --> 00:13:20.320
No!

00:13:20.840 --> 00:13:23.560
- You have to decline the engagement. - Why should I?

00:13:24.160 --> 00:13:27.879
You are just weird. Aren't you into men?

00:13:27.880 --> 00:13:29.599
Oh gosh. Mom!

00:13:29.600 --> 00:13:33.079
If you're straight, then prove it.

00:13:33.080 --> 00:13:35.239
You have to get engaged with Zafir.

00:13:35.240 --> 00:13:37.200
Radwa already has a future husband.

00:13:40.320 --> 00:13:42.599
Is that so?

00:13:42.600 --> 00:13:45.840
Okay, then I want to meet this future husband of yours.

00:13:47.520 --> 00:13:49.559
If you bring him home,

00:13:49.560 --> 00:13:51.640
you don't have to get engaged to Zafir.

00:13:52.200 --> 00:13:54.480
- I agree. - But if you fail to bring him,

00:13:55.040 --> 00:13:56.759
you have to marry Zafir immediately.

00:13:56.760 --> 00:13:58.400
Agreed.

00:14:00.160 --> 00:14:03.519
But I want to see him at your wedding!

00:14:03.520 --> 00:14:06.000
- I agree. - She agrees!

00:14:21.320 --> 00:14:23.239
- My dearest son. - Mom.

00:14:23.240 --> 00:14:25.120
You look like you're somewhere else.

00:14:27.440 --> 00:14:29.800
- Here, drink this. - Thank you, Mom.

00:14:34.040 --> 00:14:35.400
Are you okay?

00:14:36.840 --> 00:14:38.880
Are you thinking about Radwa?

00:14:42.240 --> 00:14:43.600
Auntie.

00:14:44.240 --> 00:14:45.680
Auntie?

00:14:47.520 --> 00:14:49.640
When I think about her mean behavior,

00:14:50.360 --> 00:14:53.760
I realize that Radwa's mom is way worse than her.

00:14:54.360 --> 00:14:55.560
Really?

00:14:56.280 --> 00:14:59.080
I can't let Radwa continue living like that with her mom.

00:15:00.920 --> 00:15:04.120
But didn't she say no when you proposed to her?

00:15:04.640 --> 00:15:05.800
So what are you going to do?

00:15:06.480 --> 00:15:07.999
You know me, don't you?

00:15:08.000 --> 00:15:11.080
I'll never give up and I'll give Radwa some time.

00:15:14.960 --> 00:15:18.320
Now that's my boy.

00:15:19.600 --> 00:15:21.640
So, what's your plan?

00:15:24.360 --> 00:15:26.200
Help her with her situation.

00:15:29.400 --> 00:15:31.240
Solve her problems.

00:15:39.720 --> 00:15:42.639
Just look at our youngest recruit.

00:15:42.640 --> 00:15:45.920
I told you not to come, but you insisted.

00:15:47.440 --> 00:15:50.279
- You want me to hit you or something? - Stop it.

00:15:50.280 --> 00:15:53.439
Can you calm down? I was just hyped up acting as a lawyer.

00:15:53.440 --> 00:15:56.080
Hey, can we just proceed?

00:15:57.200 --> 00:15:58.240
All right, come on.

00:16:02.080 --> 00:16:03.679
I'm Haider.

00:16:03.680 --> 00:16:06.400
Here are my colleagues, Kevin, Megat and Daniel.

00:16:07.160 --> 00:16:10.000
We are lawyers and you are being served.

00:16:11.480 --> 00:16:14.280
Four lawyers just to sue me?

00:16:16.080 --> 00:16:17.799
Who is trying to sue me?

00:16:17.800 --> 00:16:22.159
We are lawyers representing Ms. Husniya Radwa.

00:16:22.160 --> 00:16:24.199
Wow, she must be rich.

00:16:24.200 --> 00:16:26.320
She hired four lawyers?

00:16:27.200 --> 00:16:30.599
Why wouldn't she afford it?

00:16:30.600 --> 00:16:31.920
Come on, it's Radwa.

00:16:32.520 --> 00:16:33.879
Not only lawyers,

00:16:33.880 --> 00:16:36.159
but she could even hire Donald Trump if she wanted to.

00:16:36.160 --> 00:16:37.960
Her husband-to-be is rich.

00:16:38.720 --> 00:16:41.519
But why is she suing me?

00:16:41.520 --> 00:16:44.559
Because of the termination of Ms. Husniya Radwa.

00:16:44.560 --> 00:16:47.839
I have good reasoning for firing her.

00:16:47.840 --> 00:16:50.320
She wasn't terminated just because.

00:16:50.920 --> 00:16:52.320
Good reasoning?

00:16:55.840 --> 00:16:57.719
<i>- You want to slap me?</i> - Your staff was assaulted

00:16:57.720 --> 00:17:00.360
physically in the office under your supervision.

00:17:01.160 --> 00:17:02.799
She was not protected.

00:17:02.800 --> 00:17:05.119
Plus, you fired her without any investigation.

00:17:06.040 --> 00:17:10.999
We shall sue you for RM200,000

00:17:11.000 --> 00:17:14.440
for neglect of your staff's safety.

00:17:15.000 --> 00:17:17.720
Compensation for one week of absence.

00:17:18.359 --> 00:17:21.040
Electricity and water bills. Mortgage.

00:17:21.640 --> 00:17:23.880
Hire purchase loans and student loans.

00:17:24.760 --> 00:17:25.720
Chit fund contributions.

00:17:26.319 --> 00:17:29.959
Income zakat which was supposed to be paid last week.

00:17:29.960 --> 00:17:32.280
So, in total, it will be

00:17:33.240 --> 00:17:36.039
RM450,000.

00:17:36.040 --> 00:17:37.719
That's a lot.

00:17:37.720 --> 00:17:40.160
How am I supposed to come up with that much money?

00:17:47.520 --> 00:17:49.880
Husniya Radwa.

00:17:56.800 --> 00:17:58.839
So you want to give me a promotion,

00:17:58.840 --> 00:18:02.680
a raise in salary, plus additional leave?

00:18:03.440 --> 00:18:04.759
Husniya Radwa.

00:18:04.760 --> 00:18:08.959
I promise I will never take credit,

00:18:08.960 --> 00:18:12.519
slack off, or nap in the office.

00:18:12.520 --> 00:18:14.680
Really, I promise you.

00:18:16.160 --> 00:18:17.400
One more thing,

00:18:18.120 --> 00:18:22.160
if you need anything, just let me know, okay?

00:18:22.800 --> 00:18:25.200
I'll make it happen.

00:18:29.360 --> 00:18:31.280
Are you okay?

00:18:32.240 --> 00:18:38.600
This is the price I have to pay for RM450,000.

00:18:40.400 --> 00:18:42.560
You can start work next week.

00:18:46.000 --> 00:18:47.040
Thank you, boss.

00:19:08.760 --> 00:19:12.560
You mentioned I could ask for anything, right?

00:19:22.600 --> 00:19:26.000
What's the matter with you? First you agreed, now you don't?

00:19:26.760 --> 00:19:29.920
I bet you don't know why I was looking for you, do you?

00:19:31.880 --> 00:19:35.319
Your mom asked you to bring your husband-to-be

00:19:35.320 --> 00:19:37.080
to my wedding, didn't she?

00:19:46.480 --> 00:19:47.719
What's going on, Lia?

00:19:47.720 --> 00:19:49.759
My wedding is tomorrow. Can't you see right now?

00:19:49.760 --> 00:19:51.839
I still haven't settled my gown.

00:19:51.840 --> 00:19:53.359
- There's so much to do. - Tomorrow?

00:19:53.360 --> 00:19:55.319
- Tomorrow. - Where can I find a man?

00:19:55.320 --> 00:19:56.400
You have Thariq.

00:19:58.880 --> 00:20:00.839
There's no one else, Niya.

00:20:00.840 --> 00:20:02.959
- I can't, Lia. - You can.

00:20:02.960 --> 00:20:04.879
- No. - Yes.

00:20:04.880 --> 00:20:06.440
- No! - Why?

00:20:14.160 --> 00:20:17.719
- Thanks for coming. - Thanks for having me.

00:20:17.720 --> 00:20:20.080
See you later. Thank you.

00:20:21.120 --> 00:20:23.160
- Congratulations. - Thank you.

00:20:24.800 --> 00:20:26.680
I need to step down for a minute.

00:20:29.560 --> 00:20:31.960
Weddings are so tiring. So when's yours?

00:20:32.880 --> 00:20:34.520
Come on.

00:20:35.320 --> 00:20:37.680
Why was Ridz not your husband's best man?

00:20:38.440 --> 00:20:41.199
Well, he can choose whoever he wants as a best man.

00:20:41.200 --> 00:20:45.999
- None of your business. - Well, they're friends for life.

00:20:46.000 --> 00:20:47.959
Brothers from another mother.

00:20:47.960 --> 00:20:50.199
Right? Well, it was supposed to be him.

00:20:50.200 --> 00:20:52.519
He didn't come tonight because he was worried if he did,

00:20:52.520 --> 00:20:53.960
you might not want to come to my wedding.

00:20:55.240 --> 00:20:57.280
So he canceled at the very last minute.

00:20:57.880 --> 00:21:00.639
Look at how he sacrificed himself

00:21:00.640 --> 00:21:03.080
without attending his best friend's wedding.

00:21:04.920 --> 00:21:07.279
You've gone too far. I'm going to sulk.

00:21:07.280 --> 00:21:08.200
You have gone too far.

00:21:09.040 --> 00:21:12.040
So who is your future groom?

00:21:12.560 --> 00:21:14.519
Who? Do we know him?

00:21:14.520 --> 00:21:16.999
Who is it? Just tell me.

00:21:17.000 --> 00:21:19.719
- Our boss. - Oh God.

00:21:19.720 --> 00:21:21.319
Husniya Radwa. Our boss?

00:21:21.320 --> 00:21:23.359
Oh God. But he fired you.

00:21:23.360 --> 00:21:24.959
And you're hiring him to be your future groom.

00:21:24.960 --> 00:21:26.719
You know, the whole office knows

00:21:26.720 --> 00:21:29.839
Mr. Syawal Afzan wants another wife.

00:21:29.840 --> 00:21:31.399
Do you want to be his second wife?

00:21:31.400 --> 00:21:33.439
Rather than his, you might as well be my husband's second wife.

00:21:33.440 --> 00:21:35.319
Come on. You can use my husband.

00:21:35.320 --> 00:21:38.279
- You're insane. - You're crazy.

00:21:38.280 --> 00:21:39.600
Look.

00:21:42.200 --> 00:21:43.720
Mrs. Rozita.

00:21:45.680 --> 00:21:47.440
So where's your future groom?

00:21:48.480 --> 00:21:49.400
Where is he?

00:21:51.960 --> 00:21:53.480
You don't have one, do you?

00:21:54.880 --> 00:21:58.600
Remember, by the end of the month,

00:21:59.280 --> 00:22:01.520
you will marry Zafir.

00:22:02.840 --> 00:22:04.239
Mom.

00:22:04.240 --> 00:22:06.999
I bet your supposed groom is old, is he not?

00:22:07.000 --> 00:22:09.840
Old, ugly, with a round belly.

00:22:10.440 --> 00:22:12.280
You can even put coins between his teeth.

00:22:42.640 --> 00:22:44.200
Peace be upon you, Mrs. Rozita.

00:22:45.760 --> 00:22:47.240
I'm Thariq Ridzuwan.

00:22:47.960 --> 00:22:49.600
You can call me Ridz.

00:22:55.640 --> 00:22:58.319
This was my plan with Aiman. You just didn't realize it.

00:22:58.320 --> 00:23:03.160
We had asked Ridz to pretend to be your husband-to-be.

00:23:09.560 --> 00:23:10.880
Radwa.

00:23:13.960 --> 00:23:15.840
May I bring my family to meet yours?

00:23:17.160 --> 00:23:18.599
Didn't I tell you?

00:23:18.600 --> 00:23:20.919
I'm not good enough to be your wife.

00:23:20.920 --> 00:23:23.400
You are enough.

00:23:23.960 --> 00:23:25.400
Honest to God, you're enough.

00:23:28.040 --> 00:23:29.040
Okay.

00:23:29.920 --> 00:23:33.160
I can't promise that I'll solve all of your problems.

00:23:34.440 --> 00:23:36.239
But I promise

00:23:36.240 --> 00:23:38.840
you will not walk this road alone.

00:23:39.600 --> 00:23:41.679
Let me take care of you.

00:23:41.680 --> 00:23:43.880
Let me love you every moment of the day.

00:23:44.520 --> 00:23:45.920
So please.

00:23:48.680 --> 00:23:49.960
Marry me.

00:23:51.280 --> 00:23:52.800
My treasure.

00:23:58.000 --> 00:23:59.800
I'll be with you

00:24:01.280 --> 00:24:03.920
and I will always be there for you.

00:24:14.720 --> 00:24:16.559
All right, let's go straight to it.

00:24:16.560 --> 00:24:18.920
If you want to marry her,

00:24:19.800 --> 00:24:20.680
I have terms.

00:24:22.080 --> 00:24:23.200
What terms, Mom?

00:24:25.200 --> 00:24:26.440
Why didn't you discuss them with me?

00:24:33.400 --> 00:24:36.799
My sister here just got terminated.

00:24:36.800 --> 00:24:39.719
A true loser. And she thinks she has mental health problems.

00:24:39.720 --> 00:24:42.319
She's just following trends.

00:24:42.320 --> 00:24:45.119
All she does is cry and get upset.

00:24:45.120 --> 00:24:47.239
She gets sick all the time. What else?

00:24:47.240 --> 00:24:49.480
Oh, yes. She's infertile.

00:24:49.960 --> 00:24:53.919
So if you still want to marry this infertile woman,

00:24:53.920 --> 00:24:55.359
go ahead.

00:24:55.360 --> 00:24:57.320
We have a great discount for you.

00:24:59.720 --> 00:25:01.080
Give me a moment.

00:25:01.760 --> 00:25:03.800
Okay, one.

00:25:04.600 --> 00:25:07.319
There has to be a corner semi-detached house.

00:25:07.320 --> 00:25:09.359
If you can't afford that, then a bungalow.

00:25:09.360 --> 00:25:11.360
Second, a car.

00:25:12.040 --> 00:25:15.319
Preferably, a Mercedes or a BMW.

00:25:15.320 --> 00:25:19.599
Third, four handphones for all of us.

00:25:19.600 --> 00:25:23.280
Next, four holiday tickets to Europe.

00:25:24.200 --> 00:25:26.199
And don't forget to include all expenses.

00:25:26.200 --> 00:25:28.639
The last one. This is the best one.

00:25:28.640 --> 00:25:32.239
A wedding of the year at a five-star hotel.

00:25:32.240 --> 00:25:34.280
Don't forget about the dowry.

00:25:35.480 --> 00:25:37.160
RM50,000.

00:25:39.160 --> 00:25:41.279
You don't have to worry.

00:25:41.280 --> 00:25:43.079
After one year of marriage,

00:25:43.080 --> 00:25:47.680
you can claim a 10 percent rebate.

00:25:51.280 --> 00:25:53.440
Ridz, walk with me.

00:26:06.600 --> 00:26:08.080
I'm sorry.

00:26:09.840 --> 00:26:13.080
My wife and child have been very rude.

00:26:15.320 --> 00:26:16.959
Let me put it this way, Ridz.

00:26:16.960 --> 00:26:18.920
I have a little bit of savings.

00:26:19.720 --> 00:26:21.480
You can have it.

00:26:22.120 --> 00:26:23.280
Marry Radwa.

00:26:24.400 --> 00:26:28.760
Then take her far away from my lunatic family.

00:26:44.880 --> 00:26:46.280
We...

00:26:47.560 --> 00:26:50.040
We accept all the terms.

00:26:51.280 --> 00:26:55.039
We'll marry them at the end of this month. Do you agree?

00:26:55.040 --> 00:26:56.080
I agree.

00:26:56.680 --> 00:26:58.240
- Great. - Yes.

00:26:59.640 --> 00:27:01.879
Mom, let's go.

00:27:01.880 --> 00:27:03.840
Okay, we have to go.

00:27:04.600 --> 00:27:06.080
Thank you.

00:27:17.400 --> 00:27:18.920
- Sir. - Yes.

00:27:19.480 --> 00:27:20.920
Thank you.

00:27:23.720 --> 00:27:25.560
May I know your name?

00:27:26.160 --> 00:27:28.600
- Raudhah. - Raudhah.

00:27:30.080 --> 00:27:31.559
You have a beautiful name.

00:27:31.560 --> 00:27:33.839
But it doesn't suit your attitude.

00:27:33.840 --> 00:27:35.680
Who taught you manners?

00:27:36.640 --> 00:27:38.480
The devil?

00:27:56.000 --> 00:27:57.880
New intel on Chi Beng.

00:27:59.520 --> 00:28:01.360
Meet up with a new buyer.

00:28:02.840 --> 00:28:04.360
All the details are in the file.

00:28:10.240 --> 00:28:11.879
We'll go on a full stakeout

00:28:11.880 --> 00:28:15.240
starting tonight until the meet-up.

00:28:15.920 --> 00:28:16.959
All clear?

00:28:16.960 --> 00:28:18.600
- Clear. - Clear.

00:28:21.600 --> 00:28:22.680
Ridz.

00:28:23.720 --> 00:28:26.520
Our meeting is a day before your wedding.

00:28:27.320 --> 00:28:28.560
You should sit out this mission.

00:28:40.360 --> 00:28:42.720
You'll return a day before our wedding?

00:28:45.160 --> 00:28:47.240
Don't you want to postpone our wedding?

00:28:47.840 --> 00:28:49.839
No, why should we?

00:28:49.840 --> 00:28:51.240
I'll come back in time.

00:28:54.600 --> 00:28:56.160
You're about to go on a dangerous mission.

00:28:56.920 --> 00:28:59.599
I don't want you to rush and lose focus.

00:28:59.600 --> 00:29:01.360
It's dangerous, dude.

00:29:06.640 --> 00:29:07.920
Who is this "dude?"

00:29:16.480 --> 00:29:17.800
It doesn't seem like there's anyone else here.

00:29:25.720 --> 00:29:28.400
Dude, don't get upset.

00:29:30.960 --> 00:29:32.599
Excuse me.

00:29:32.600 --> 00:29:34.519
I'm talking to you.

00:29:34.520 --> 00:29:35.759
Are you a mute?

00:29:35.760 --> 00:29:37.200
Radwa.

00:29:38.560 --> 00:29:40.319
We're about to get married.

00:29:40.320 --> 00:29:42.600
Why are you still speaking to me casually?

00:29:43.680 --> 00:29:45.399
Casual is fine, is it not?

00:29:45.400 --> 00:29:48.080
Do we need to change that? No, it's fine.

00:29:48.680 --> 00:29:51.759
All right, can you imagine?

00:29:51.760 --> 00:29:53.879
We'll be praying together after we're married.

00:29:53.880 --> 00:29:56.679
So after our prayers, I will pray, "O Allah, O God,

00:29:56.680 --> 00:29:59.440
bless me with a stubborn..."

00:30:02.480 --> 00:30:07.879
"A wife who is kind, demure, and graceful."

00:30:07.880 --> 00:30:10.559
Then I'll end my prayer.

00:30:10.560 --> 00:30:12.679
Then you approach me and say,

00:30:12.680 --> 00:30:15.120
"Oh, my most beloved husband,

00:30:16.080 --> 00:30:18.039
what do you want for dinner, dude?"

00:30:18.040 --> 00:30:20.160
Does that not sound disrespectful? Please, come on.

00:30:24.240 --> 00:30:26.279
Dude is just fine.

00:30:26.280 --> 00:30:27.480
That's what you call rare.

00:30:28.080 --> 00:30:29.320
Am I right?

00:30:31.880 --> 00:30:34.080
All right, come over here.

00:30:34.920 --> 00:30:37.640
Sit. Let's talk about it.

00:30:38.560 --> 00:30:40.240
What would you like me to call you?

00:30:42.440 --> 00:30:44.720
But promise me you'll call me that.

00:30:46.480 --> 00:30:48.039
- Okay, I promise. - Promise me.

00:30:48.040 --> 00:30:51.159
Because I've already made up my mind.

00:30:51.160 --> 00:30:52.960
I want you to call me...

00:30:55.280 --> 00:30:56.320
Bad Papa.

00:30:57.080 --> 00:30:58.840
And I will call you

00:30:59.440 --> 00:31:00.760
Mama Love.

00:31:04.000 --> 00:31:06.399
What are you laughing at?

00:31:06.400 --> 00:31:08.560
Your punchline is so silly.

00:31:09.400 --> 00:31:10.920
Oh, silly?

00:31:20.520 --> 00:31:21.440
Oh my God.

00:31:24.720 --> 00:31:25.840
This is real?

00:31:26.680 --> 00:31:28.759
- This is real. - This is really real?

00:31:28.760 --> 00:31:30.080
Yeah. Why?

00:31:30.800 --> 00:31:32.520
Us? Getting married?

00:31:33.160 --> 00:31:34.800
- We're getting married? - Yes.

00:31:36.920 --> 00:31:40.199
The problem is, I haven't prepared anything.

00:31:40.200 --> 00:31:43.079
The forms, the hall, my dress. My dress.

00:31:43.080 --> 00:31:45.080
- Witnesses. - Radwa.

00:31:45.680 --> 00:31:48.240
You won't be here. Dahlia's on her honeymoon.

00:31:48.760 --> 00:31:50.840
- It's just me. - Treasure.

00:31:56.600 --> 00:31:58.680
I've arranged everything.

00:32:09.640 --> 00:32:10.960
Come back safely.

00:32:15.960 --> 00:32:17.800
Thariq Ridzuwan.

00:32:20.680 --> 00:32:22.400
Promise me?

00:32:45.200 --> 00:32:46.720
Can you walk normally?

00:32:47.480 --> 00:32:50.719
- Why? - We're the Holy Dragon.

00:32:50.720 --> 00:32:52.719
- Smart. - Okay.

00:32:52.720 --> 00:32:54.200
Okay.

00:33:05.520 --> 00:33:06.600
Boys.

00:33:07.640 --> 00:33:11.840
Daniel and I have found Chi Beng's location.

00:33:12.800 --> 00:33:14.280
Here.

00:33:15.200 --> 00:33:17.240
The place I scoped out

00:33:17.880 --> 00:33:19.639
is Chi Beng's hideout.

00:33:19.640 --> 00:33:22.279
Eleven pictures, and eleven locations.

00:33:22.280 --> 00:33:24.280
Now we just have to wait for further instructions.

00:33:25.320 --> 00:33:27.840
Here's what we'll do. We've determined the location.

00:33:29.360 --> 00:33:30.880
We will enter through here.

00:33:31.560 --> 00:33:34.999
After this point, I believe he will be in this room.

00:33:35.000 --> 00:33:37.079
We will arrest him as soon as we arrive.

00:33:37.080 --> 00:33:39.200
- Clear? - Clear.

00:33:44.160 --> 00:33:45.760
Lia!

00:33:47.960 --> 00:33:51.239
I'm back!

00:33:51.240 --> 00:33:53.160
Oh my God!

00:33:54.760 --> 00:33:56.879
Lia, I thought you would come back in three days.

00:33:56.880 --> 00:33:59.039
I asked Aiman to shorten our honeymoon

00:33:59.040 --> 00:34:01.559
because I wanted to help my best friend here.

00:34:01.560 --> 00:34:03.959
Besides, he has a mission.

00:34:03.960 --> 00:34:06.199
- You're getting married! - Thank you, Lia.

00:34:06.200 --> 00:34:08.120
You're welcome.

00:34:08.800 --> 00:34:11.238
Okay, so how are your preparations going?

00:34:11.239 --> 00:34:13.000
Perfect.

00:34:13.760 --> 00:34:16.079
- You're getting married! - Yes, I'm getting married!

00:34:16.080 --> 00:34:18.439
- Let's go inside. - Come on and have a look.

00:34:18.440 --> 00:34:20.079
See what I've done so far.

00:34:20.080 --> 00:34:22.520
Oh my God!

00:34:23.040 --> 00:34:25.559
I can't wait to see you in your wedding gown!

00:34:25.560 --> 00:34:27.960
I knew it. It's Thariq, right?

00:34:28.480 --> 00:34:31.719
I knew you were going to end up with Thariq Ridzuwan.

00:34:34.320 --> 00:34:36.919
- Okay, we have the ring. - What's all this?

00:34:36.920 --> 00:34:38.560
Why is there so much stuff in my way?

00:34:40.320 --> 00:34:42.520
- Hey! - What's your problem?

00:34:43.560 --> 00:34:46.400
I'm sorry. I did it on purpose.

00:34:50.360 --> 00:34:52.040
Just ignore her.

00:34:53.679 --> 00:34:56.360
Lia, you know me, right?

00:34:57.360 --> 00:34:59.040
Once my bad luck starts,

00:34:59.600 --> 00:35:02.040
everything will fall apart.

00:35:02.640 --> 00:35:04.559
You can't think that way.

00:35:04.560 --> 00:35:07.120
What else can that lunatic ruin in this house?

00:35:09.360 --> 00:35:11.239
I don't think there is anything left.

00:35:11.240 --> 00:35:13.840
I left my wedding gown with Thariq's mom.

00:35:30.000 --> 00:35:31.760
Go ahead and ruin it.

00:35:40.080 --> 00:35:42.559
Serves you right, Niya.

00:35:42.560 --> 00:35:44.680
So, you want to get married, huh?

00:35:49.320 --> 00:35:52.759
- Hey, let go of me! - Stand here.

00:35:52.760 --> 00:35:55.359
- Don't you know the rules? - Who's the jerk who proposed to you?

00:35:55.360 --> 00:35:57.159
- Why did you accept him? - The jerk?

00:35:57.160 --> 00:36:02.879
That is what you call an animal like you.

00:36:02.880 --> 00:36:05.560
Husniya, I have no time to fool around. Who is that guy?

00:36:06.280 --> 00:36:07.679
Thariq Ridzuwan. My fiancé.

00:36:07.680 --> 00:36:09.799
Why did I accept him? None of your business!

00:36:09.800 --> 00:36:12.159
You rejected me because of that guy?

00:36:12.160 --> 00:36:17.279
I rejected you because you're a pervert.

00:36:17.280 --> 00:36:19.799
You're fake, self-centered and a walking red flag.

00:36:19.800 --> 00:36:21.999
Are you insulting me?

00:36:22.000 --> 00:36:24.159
I'm not insulting you. I'm just speaking my mind.

00:36:24.160 --> 00:36:26.760
I pray that you quickly repent.

00:36:28.240 --> 00:36:31.719
So you'll accept me if I repent? Is that it?

00:36:31.720 --> 00:36:33.599
If you're willing to share me with Thariq,

00:36:33.600 --> 00:36:36.679
being a second husband, that's fine with me.

00:36:36.680 --> 00:36:39.159
I'm not done yet, Husniya Radwa.

00:36:39.160 --> 00:36:41.959
I really hate

00:36:41.960 --> 00:36:44.120
people yelling at me.

00:36:45.760 --> 00:36:47.359
Remember this, Husniya.

00:36:47.360 --> 00:36:49.639
I've been waiting five years for you.

00:36:49.640 --> 00:36:50.720
Five years.

00:36:51.600 --> 00:36:54.639
I will do whatever it takes

00:36:54.640 --> 00:36:58.400
for you to be my wife.

00:37:00.920 --> 00:37:04.480
I can ruin your wedding anytime I want.

00:37:05.920 --> 00:37:07.520
Remember that.

00:37:18.840 --> 00:37:20.080
Hello, auntie.

00:37:20.800 --> 00:37:22.200
What?

00:37:43.560 --> 00:37:46.160
Maybe this is a sign, auntie.

00:37:47.080 --> 00:37:49.360
What do you mean, Radwa?

00:37:51.640 --> 00:37:54.199
I should not marry Ridz.

00:37:54.200 --> 00:37:56.559
What are you talking about?

00:37:56.560 --> 00:37:58.119
What are you saying?

00:37:58.120 --> 00:38:01.359
Because...

00:38:01.360 --> 00:38:04.519
You need to calm down. Just try to calm down, okay?

00:38:04.520 --> 00:38:09.640
When you've calmed down, you can tell me about it, okay?

00:38:22.200 --> 00:38:24.879
I seek refuge in God from the accursed Satan.

00:38:24.880 --> 00:38:27.399
In the name of God, the Most Gracious, the Most Merciful.

00:38:27.400 --> 00:38:30.839
In the name of God, with whose name

00:38:30.840 --> 00:38:33.639
nothing on earth or in the heavens can cause harm,

00:38:33.640 --> 00:38:35.799
and He is the All-Hearing and All-Knowing.

00:38:35.800 --> 00:38:37.440
Amen.

00:38:40.360 --> 00:38:42.599
There is no deity except You.

00:38:42.600 --> 00:38:46.319
<i>Exalted are You. Indeed, I have been one of the wrongdoers.</i>

00:38:46.320 --> 00:38:48.879
<i>There is no deity except God.</i>

00:38:48.880 --> 00:38:51.480
<i>Muhammad is His Messenger.</i>

00:39:41.960 --> 00:39:43.680
Target has arrived.

00:39:45.000 --> 00:39:46.080
Let's go.

00:40:41.440 --> 00:40:43.879
Can you not give me some space to breathe?

00:40:43.880 --> 00:40:45.920
You're a child smuggler.

00:40:47.440 --> 00:40:49.720
I will hunt you down to your grave.

00:40:50.640 --> 00:40:55.520
So you think those kids care about you?

00:41:18.480 --> 00:41:20.520
I like your style, baby.

00:42:52.080 --> 00:42:54.039
- Have you called Thariq? - Yeah.

00:42:54.040 --> 00:42:56.079
- So? - He's not answering.

00:42:56.080 --> 00:42:57.959
His mom?

00:42:57.960 --> 00:42:59.640
- She's not answering either. - Gosh.

00:43:00.560 --> 00:43:02.240
Maybe they are on their way.

00:43:02.840 --> 00:43:04.479
I hope so, Lia.

00:43:04.480 --> 00:43:06.919
Poor girl.

00:43:06.920 --> 00:43:09.599
You prepared the wedding gifts all by yourself.

00:43:09.600 --> 00:43:12.959
On your wedding day, there's no sign of your groom.

00:43:12.960 --> 00:43:15.079
Does he really want to marry you?

00:43:15.080 --> 00:43:18.599
He's running late because of work. He is out there saving the nation.

00:43:18.600 --> 00:43:20.560
Is that so?

00:43:21.280 --> 00:43:22.479
Oh my God.

00:43:22.480 --> 00:43:26.679
Maybe he's fooling around with another woman there.

00:43:26.680 --> 00:43:28.560
Of course he's fooling around.

00:43:29.360 --> 00:43:32.479
- Right. - Special forces men are players.

00:43:32.480 --> 00:43:33.999
Do you not know that?

00:43:34.000 --> 00:43:35.279
Don't you know?

00:43:35.280 --> 00:43:38.960
On social media, most men who work in that line

00:43:39.680 --> 00:43:41.159
tend to sleep around.

00:43:41.160 --> 00:43:43.560
Now it seems like you're the one who's eager to get married.

00:43:45.240 --> 00:43:47.200
What? Do you think I'm not boiling in this dress?

00:43:47.960 --> 00:43:49.480
Enough!

00:43:52.360 --> 00:43:55.199
It seems like

00:43:55.200 --> 00:43:58.920
you're trying to embarrass me in front of everyone.

00:44:00.720 --> 00:44:02.240
No, Mom.

00:44:02.760 --> 00:44:04.279
Peace be upon you.

00:44:04.280 --> 00:44:05.880
They're here.

00:44:08.720 --> 00:44:10.319
Please, come in.

00:44:10.320 --> 00:44:11.920
Have a seat.

00:44:18.120 --> 00:44:20.080
You look gorgeous.

00:44:20.640 --> 00:44:22.360
I don't think so.

00:44:30.840 --> 00:44:32.120
So where is Thariq Ridzuwan?

00:44:34.800 --> 00:44:37.160
He...

00:44:38.440 --> 00:44:41.359
Don't try to make a fool of me.

00:44:41.360 --> 00:44:44.159
How can the wedding continue without a groom?

00:44:44.160 --> 00:44:46.719
Has the groom gone missing?

00:44:46.720 --> 00:44:48.360
He backed out?

00:44:49.200 --> 00:44:50.479
Then cancel the wedding.

00:44:50.480 --> 00:44:52.559
Tell everyone to leave.

00:44:52.560 --> 00:44:54.840
It's embarrassing to wait here this long.

00:44:55.520 --> 00:44:57.320
No, we're not canceling.

00:44:58.480 --> 00:45:01.039
Right, please don't cancel.

00:45:01.040 --> 00:45:03.240
Can we give him a little more time?

00:45:04.000 --> 00:45:06.040
I'm not canceling, but I cannot wait.

00:45:06.920 --> 00:45:08.880
If your son fails to marry my daughter,

00:45:09.480 --> 00:45:12.360
I have my own son-in-law of choice.

00:45:14.360 --> 00:45:18.600
Hey, don't embarrass Ridz's family.

00:45:19.520 --> 00:45:20.440
Quiet.

00:45:21.320 --> 00:45:23.119
Who is embarrassing whom right now?

00:45:23.120 --> 00:45:24.799
She is the one who's embarrassing us.

00:45:24.800 --> 00:45:27.079
She came here without her son.

00:45:27.080 --> 00:45:29.080
How can our daughter get married?

00:45:33.000 --> 00:45:34.680
Zafir.

00:45:47.080 --> 00:45:48.440
Peace be upon you, my wife.

00:45:52.640 --> 00:45:57.080
{\an8}TO BE CONTINUED

00:46:04.400 --> 00:46:05.639
{\an8}<i>If you want help,</i>

00:46:05.640 --> 00:46:07.559
{\an8}<i>don't ask me.</i>

00:46:07.560 --> 00:46:09.879
{\an8}<i>Go and ask the police for help!</i>

00:46:09.880 --> 00:46:12.719
{\an8}Auntie, I am terribly sorry.

00:46:12.720 --> 00:46:14.559
{\an8}NEXT EPISODE PREVIEW

00:46:14.560 --> 00:46:17.559
{\an8}It seems my respect for you is fading.

00:46:17.560 --> 00:46:19.280
{\an8}Hey, what's the matter?

00:46:19.880 --> 00:46:22.000
{\an8}It feels like someone is watching us.

00:46:22.600 --> 00:46:24.800
{\an8}I have been kidnapped.

00:46:25.520 --> 00:46:27.080
{\an8}How could I possibly feel happy?

00:46:29.840 --> 00:46:32.640
{\an8}Radwa and Ridz. Do you want me to break them up?

